  "detailed_description": "<h1>Other Games From Taiwan Indie Devs!</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378350/extras/851659b1127902e4f3280f7bb23cb116.poster.avif?t=1640096333\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378350/extras/851659b1127902e4f3280f7bb23cb116.webm?t=1640096333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378350/extras/851659b1127902e4f3280f7bb23cb116.mp4?t=1640096333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Drifting : Weight of Feathers》</h2><br>A third-person-action game with a special emphasis on aerial-combat. Players need to utilize grappling hook and acrobatics to fight enemies, solve puzzles to progress through each level.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Third-person fast-paced action</strong><br></li><li><strong>Fluid animation and versatile control system</strong><br></li><li><strong>Customizable hair options for Faye</strong><br></li><li><strong>Physics based puzzle solving</strong><br></li><li><strong>Parkour on whale!</strong> ヽ（・∀・）ノ <br></li><li><strong>Steep learning curve, very hardcore! Play with caution!</strong> Σ( ° △ °|||)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378350/extras/4cde5d3bb19833b1ff0f982b66ba8c08.poster.avif?t=1640096333\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378350/extras/4cde5d3bb19833b1ff0f982b66ba8c08.webm?t=1640096333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378350/extras/4cde5d3bb19833b1ff0f982b66ba8c08.mp4?t=1640096333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Download  《Drifting : Weight of Feathers》 demo and experience it yourself!",
